        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: 'The extra thing I asked you to prepare, how is it coming along, Asimov?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Had a few hiccups. Still working on it.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'As you know, the Task Force classifies combat zones based on their Punishing Virus intensity.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Most people are familiar with the three major categories of combat zones: high, middle, and low. But there\\'s a fourth: Dead Zones.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'A lot can be said about Dead Zones, but to sum it up in one sentence: we can\\'t go in there unprotected—not even after we get a serum injection.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'So, in order to protect the M.I.N.D. stability of Constructs in Dead Zones, we\\'ve upgraded the link chamber.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'I will spare you the details about the link chamber. All you need to know, which you already do, is that it\\'s a machine that allows Commandant to command Constructs remotely.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'I heard you\\'ve tried remote command on several teams now.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Only a handful... And we expect that only Cerberus will adopt the technique in the end.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Ever since remote connection was abolished, it has been excluded by military schools from Commandant assessment criteria. As a result, the available sample are few and far between.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Most of the registered Commandants have no access to the link chamber. Even if they do—', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'The Constructs still have their limitations. They can only get to the outermost part of a Dead Zone. If they try going any deeper, malfunctions occur immediately...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'So do you mean to tell me that the program has failed, Asimov?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: '\"Fail\" is a word I never said and never will say.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Me and my technicians are ready to move on to phase two. We have plenty of time to pick a Commandant, but right now we need to have the Constructs overhauled.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'Overhaul? The way you did with Gray Raven\\'s Constructs?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Only more radical... I\\'m going to develop new models that are truly fit for purpose.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Nikola', 3: 'And how do you plan to do it?', 4: '2'}"
    },
